  }, "About Sense"), mdx("p", null, "Sense was started to attend to the need to produce an information networking fabric that is used to support a complex language model, that's in-turn employed for various foundational applications. The project requires works in various different fields, which contribute towards the derivative purpose of producing foundational technological infrastructure that works as a fabric, whilst supporting local private use & related characteristics as is necessary to materially support ", mdx("a", {
